body:
The following query returns only the metadata in the results.

**Input:**

```json
db.fruit.aggregate([
  {
    "$searchMeta": {
      "facet": {
        "operator": {
          "compound": {
            "must": [{
              "text": {
                "query": "varieties",
                "path": "description"
              }
            }],
            "should": [{
              "text": {
                "query": "Fuji",
                "path": "description"
              }
            }]
          }
        },
        "facets": {
          "categoryFacet": {
            "type": "string",
            "path": "category"
          }
        }
      }
    }
  }
])
```

**Output:**

```javascript
[
  {
    count: { lowerBound: Long('2') },
    facet: {
      categoryFacet: {
        buckets: [
          { _id: 'nonorganic', count: Long('1') },
          { _id: 'organic', count: Long('1') }
        ]
      }
    }
  }
]
```

